text: Bianca Jade Gascoigne (born October 28, 1986) is an English glamour model and reality television personality. Gascoigne is the daughter of television personality Sheryl Gascoigne and the adopted daughter of former footballer Paul Gascoigne. She has a brother Mason and a half-brother Regan Gascoigne. In 2006, Bianca Gascoigne won the second series of Celebrity Love Island. She is also well-known for being a contestant on season 19 of Celebrity Big Brother in 2017.
